any|website=cbrn-liberec.army.cz|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n** 311st Radiological, Chemical and Biological Protection Battalion (''311. Prapor Radia\u010dn\u00ed, Chemick\u00e9 a Biologick\u00e9 Ochrany'') <ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.armedconflicts.com/311th-Radiation-Chemical-and-Biological-Defense-Battalion-t63609|title=311. prapor radia\u010dn\u00ed, chemick\u00e9 a biologick\u00e9 ochrany|website=armedconflicts.com|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n**312th Radiological, Chemical and Biological Protection Battalion (''312. Prapor Radia\u010dn\u00ed, Chemick\u00e9 a Biologick\u00e9 Ochrany'') <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.armedconflicts.com/312th-Radiation-Chemical-and-Biological-Defense-Battalion-t63610|title=312. prapor radia\u010dn\u00ed, chemick\u00e9 a biologick\u00e9 ochrany|website=armedconflicts.com|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n** 314th Weapons of Mass Destruction Center (''314. Centrum V\u00fdstrahy Zbran\u00ed Hromadn\u00e9ho Ni\u010den\u00ed'') <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.armedconflicts.com/314th-Weapons-of-Mass-Dectruction-Warning-Centre-t63611|title=314. centrum v\u00fdstrahy zbran\u00ed hromadn\u00e9ho ni\u010den\u00ed|website=armedconflicts.com|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Denmark==\n* 3rd Chemical Biological Radiological Nuclear and Construction Battalion (''3 Kemisk Biologisk Radiologisk Atomar & Konstruktionsbataljon'') <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www2.forsvaret.dk/omos/organisation/haeren/organisation/ingenioerregimentet/Pages/3_CBRN_KONSTBTN.aspx\n|title=3 CBRN & KONSTBTN |website=forsvaret.dk|date=13 September 2018|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Finland==\n* Protection Company \u2013 Engineer and Signal Battalion \u201cSatakunta\u201d (''Suojelukomppania - Satakunnan Pioneeri- ja Viestipataljoona'') <ref>{{cite web|url=https://maavoimat.fi/porin-prikaati/varusmiehena-meilla\n|title=Satakunnan pioneeri- ja viestipataljoonassa|website=maavoimat.fi|date=|accessdate=17 April 2020}}</re